content.p: • To enable graduates, following relevant industrial training and experience, to become chartered/professional engineers with demonstration of good knowledge and understanding of chemical engineering theory, methods and practice. • To produce graduates who can gain senior, supervisory and management positions in their chosen industries/fields. • To enable graduates to participate in and benefit from lifelong learning. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8001
